This person keeps causing all these problems but Harry ignores them and does nothing about it. Harry only realizes how bad these problems are when they get so bad it seems unfixable. Pretty much this person causes all these problems but harry just can’t seem to leave the person no matter how bad it gets.

snippet.textDisplay: one of the most enchanting things about love is that even if it hurts u, even if u're suffering from immense pain, u're still in *love*. it's just so pure, that u wouldn't trade the feeling of being in love for anything in the world. even if it hurts, u'll prefer to be in love than to fall out of love. i think that's what the mv portrayed perfectly. he was drowning in love, & instead of choosing to save himself by swimming up to the surface, he chose to stay in love, to drown in love, because there's nothing more beautiful than falling in love, because there's nothing more beautiful than love, itself.

snippet.textDisplay: During the Video at 0:40 I’m pretty sure one of those rings is Camille’s. Also at 2:14 you can see the Eiffel Tower outside of the window, which is in France, Where Camille is from. On the piano you can see a ship, I’m not quite sure what it resembles. There’s 4 other objects on it as far as I know and I’m not sure what they are yet. I think one may be a fish, and another a sea-star or just a star. The fish may resemble the fish from Adore You; that fish would probably resemble Camille. There’s a portrait of a King or something. It’s not King Louis, I know that. I think there’s 3 other paintings on the walls as well; each of them with a king or queen on it I’m pretty sure; I’m not positive on it. Something inside/on top of the piano at 0:47 may be words or not, I’m confused by it but looking into it. The water does resemble depression, if you can’t tell that yet.

snippet.textDisplay: This song speaks to me on another level. I got a boyfriend 7 months ago and back then I finally  came over my depression just right before I met him. I had goals in my life and all I wanted to be was: happy. He is one year older than me and just started university last year. I was planning to  go too this year after middle school. That was my biig big big dream. And then when I told him that, my bigest dream of all he said he would leave me because that university is not near him and it's not okay for us not to meet all the time. I'm barerly with my dad who I miss so much and who can die anytime bc he is sick. But he won't care... He said I have to work and go to the university where he goes. That was enough for me and I wanted to break up. Then he treathened me with his death if I break up with him. I lost my dreams, my self-confidence. He promised he would se a phycologist, hell he never did. I'm crying myself to sleep, I hate him for taking the things are care about the most from me
